## Change Log Usage Instructions

- Add each new update or patch in reverse chronological order (newest first).
- Reference specific files/directories and note if ZIP/PromptPack content was integrated.
- For significant changes, describe the impact on workflow or prompt authoring.
- Minor typo fixes or style edits may be batched as a single entry.

